TY  - JOUR
TI  - Equilibrium in a Production Economy with an Income Tax
AU  - Coleman, Wilbur John
AB  - [A state-dependent income tax is incorporated into a stochastic, discrete-time, infinite-horizon production economy. Methods are developed for establishing the existence and uniqueness of an equilibrium, and for computing this equilibrium.]
